::GoldenEye:;

She smiled as he took her hand.  Why would a bot, whom she had just 
met suddenly show her such affection as he was.  Her instincts told 
her to be causous.  But her spark told her to enjoy the moment.

She smiled and walked with him.


Time lapse::::::::

They finally reach the pod and she turned to him. "Can you fly this 
thing or do you want me to?" she smiled.
